            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E6%A6%B4%E8%8E%B2%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%87200%E5%85%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E6%A6%B4%E8%8E%B2%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%87200%E5%85%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃榴莲每天不要超过200克#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%A6%B4%E8%8E%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%A6%B4%E8%8E%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么榴莲不能多吃#</span></a> <br><br>榴莲闻着臭吃起来香，每100克榴莲含有蛋白质2.6克、脂肪3.3克，几乎和牛奶相当。不过，榴莲好吃但不能多吃，《中国居民膳食指南》建议每天吃水果200到350克，但榴莲属于特殊的水果，建议每天食用量不要超过200克。另外，减肥人群也要控制榴莲的摄入量。（央视网）<br><br>一个小问题，你喜欢吃榴莲吗？让我来瞧瞧卫粉里“榴莲党”多还是“反榴莲党”多<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6NJCaZo" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
