            <title><![CDATA[#脂肪肝继续发展会怎么样#【注意！#脂肪肝导致的肝癌正在增加#[吃惊]】脂肪肝早期没有明显外在症状，常被大家忽视。数据显示，我国成年人脂肪肝患病率已达30%至4...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BC%9A%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E4%BC%9A%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#脂肪肝继续发展会怎么样#</span></a>【注意！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%84%82%E8%82%AA%E8%82%9D%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#脂肪肝导致的肝癌正在增加#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】脂肪肝早期没有明显外在症状，常被大家忽视。数据显示，我国成年人脂肪肝患病率已达30%至40%。脂肪肝早期不痛不痒，但若覆盖肝脏的脂肪越来越多，肝脏炎症持续发作，或致脂肪性肝硬化，进而引发癌变。如何干预脂肪肝，避免肝癌发生？👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4892706909126715" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hd6grur0hyj61je0v6e8102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/wDDrcpz5lx084OW1tUD601041200nkeV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1682111794&amp;ssig=m1WtE7WAe0&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/bami22kVlx084OW0VLVu01041200c8KA0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1682111794&amp;ssig=WTboo8B%2FC8&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ApAbuRCxlx084OW0BuiQ010412007G3z0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1682111794&amp;ssig=weynGMa8wl&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4892706909126715&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
