            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%80%E5%BE%80%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃癌早期往往没有典型症状#</span></a> 】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E7%9B%90%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E7%9B%90%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E8%83%83%E7%99%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃太多盐增加胃癌风险#</span></a> 据国家癌症中心统计，我国胃癌发病率位列所有恶性肿瘤第二位，男性发病率是女性的两倍以上。胃癌早期常常没有特异性症状，大多数由胃溃疡发展而来。腌制品、烟熏食品、霉变食品以及过多摄入食盐可增加胃癌风险。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F5%E4%B8%AA%E6%8A%A5%E8%AD%A6%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F5%E4%B8%AA%E6%8A%A5%E8%AD%A6%E4%BF%A1%E5%8F%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肿瘤早期5个报警信号#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6Nx7q6Q" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
